{"product_id":"drip-athletic-dry-fit-black","title":"BLACK DRY-FIT","description":"\u003cp\u003eLightweight Fabric. Slim Fit. Crewneck. 100% Recycled Polyester. Dry Fit Performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis slim-fit T-shirt is designed for comfort and performance across all athletic activities. Crafted from lightweight recycled polyester, it stays soft against the skin while allowing free and easy movement. The Dry Fit fabric helps wick away moisture to keep you feeling dry and comfortable during training, workouts, or active routines. Finished with a classic crewneck and a clean, athletic silhouette, this tee delivers a sleek look that supports performance without compromising comfort.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash with similar colors in cold water. Avoid fabric softeners to maintain moisture-wicking performance. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightweight recycled polyester fabric for breathability and comfort. Slim fit that stays close to the body for a streamlined look and unrestricted movement. Classic crewneck design for versatile athletic wear. Dry Fit technology helps keep you dry during any athletic activity. True to size—recommended to order your usual size.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064627019930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064627052698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064627085466,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064627118234,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00715copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440796","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/drip-athletic-dry-fit-black","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}